# Azure Authentication Settings for Microsoft Sentinel
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your credentials

# Your Azure Active Directory (tenant) ID 
TENANT_ID=your_tenant_id_here

# Your Azure AD application (client) ID
CLIENT_ID=your_client_id_here

# Your Azure AD application secret
CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret_here

# Your Log Analytics workspace ID
WORKSPACE_ID=your_workspace_id_here

# The application requires the following Azure permissions:
# - Log Analytics API: Read access to Log Analytics workspaces
# - Microsoft Sentinel: Reader role or higher

# How to obtain these credentials:
# 1. Register an application in Azure AD
# 2. Create a client secret for the application
# 3. Grant the application access to your Log Analytics workspace
# 4. Grant the application the Sentinel Reader role or higher 